{"thag6.3:0.1":"Theragatha 6.3 ","thag6.3:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thag6.3:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag6.3:0.4":"Mahanagattheragatha ","thag6.3:1.1":"“Yassa sabrahmacarisu, ","thag6.3:1.2":"garavo nupalabbhati; ","thag6.3:1.3":"Parihayati saddhamma, ","thag6.3:1.4":"maccho appodake yatha. ","thag6.3:2.1":"Yassa sabrahmacarisu, ","thag6.3:2.2":"garavo nupalabbhati; ","thag6.3:2.3":"Na viruhati saddhamme, ","thag6.3:2.4":"khette bijamva putikam. ","thag6.3:3.1":"Yassa sabrahmacarisu, ","thag6.3:3.2":"garavo nupalabbhati; ","thag6.3:3.3":"Araka hoti nibbana, ","thag6.3:3.4":"dhammarajassa sasane. ","thag6.3:4.1":"Yassa sabrahmacarisu, ","thag6.3:4.2":"garavo upalabbhati; ","thag6.3:4.3":"Na vihayati saddhamma, ","thag6.3:4.4":"maccho bavhodake yatha. ","thag6.3:5.1":"Yassa sabrahmacarisu, ","thag6.3:5.2":"garavo upalabbhati; ","thag6.3:5.3":"So viruhati saddhamme, ","thag6.3:5.4":"khette bijamva bhaddakam. ","thag6.3:6.1":"Yassa sabrahmacarisu, ","thag6.3:6.2":"garavo upalabbhati; ","thag6.3:6.3":"Santike hoti nibbanam, ","thag6.3:6.4":"dhammarajassa sasane”ti. ","thag6.3:6.5":"… Mahanago thero …. "}